363
00:51:45,390 --> 00:51:54,540
Naredili boste napake in nato boste imeli problem vi in vaš pacient.

364
00:51:54,640 --> 00:51:59,140
Ne samo pacient, tudi vi boste imeli problem.

365
00:51:59,890 --> 00:52:13,140
